      <title>巴克莱家族向劳埃德银行偿还 12 亿英镑电报贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/lloyds-repaid-by-barclay-family-for-1-2-billion-telegraph-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳埃德银行集团 (Lloyds Banking Group Plc) 已从《电讯报》所有者处获得 12 亿英镑（合 15 亿美元），这标志着该银行不再卷入一场引发政府调查并引发全国范围内有关新闻自由讨论的事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/lloyds-repaid-by-barclay-family-for-1-2-billion-telegraph-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 13:33:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Spotify 裁员 1,500 人，首席执行官 Ek 表示流媒体必须更加精简</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/spotify-will-cut-headcount-by-17-to-confront-slower-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Spotify Technology SA 将裁员 17%，这是该公司今年最大幅度的裁员，这是削减成本和提高盈利能力的积极努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/spotify-will-cut-headcount-by-17-to-confront-slower-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 07:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆集团着眼于资产出售、削减成本以修复汽车部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/continental-under-pressure-to-find-ev-path-after-stumbles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大陆集团正在评估资产出售，并将削减额外成本以保护回报并扭转其落后于同行的关键汽车部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/continental-under-pressure-to-find-ev-path-after-stumbles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管股票和债券遭受重创，比特币仍飙升至 42,000 美元以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/bitcoin-hits-40-000-level-for-the-first-time-since-may-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市在经历了几周的强势之后，周一表现不佳。债券市场上也有类似的情况。金价在攀升至每盎司 2,100 美元以上的新纪录后出现了 180 度大转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/bitcoin-hits-40-000-level-for-the-first-time-since-may-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 22:39:57 GMT</pubDate>
